Class CustomDeclaredType

java.lang.Object
com.mackenziehigh.autumn.lang.compiler.typesystem.AbstractType
com.mackenziehigh.autumn.lang.compiler.typesystem.AbstractDeclaredType
com.mackenziehigh.autumn.lang.compiler.typesystem.CustomDeclaredType
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAnnotatable, IAnnotationType, IClassType, IDeclaredType, IElementType, IEnumType, IExpressionType, IInterfaceType, IReferenceType, IReturnType, IType, IVariableType, ICustomAnnotatable
public final class CustomDeclaredType extends AbstractDeclaredType implements IAnnotationType, IClassType, IEnumType, IInterfaceType, ICustomAnnotatable
An instance of this class represents a declared type.
